name: Aurora S01
description: Aurora Borealis Series 01, earths rarest and most incredible natural light display. Auroras are the result of disturbances in the magnetosphere caused by solar wind. These disturbances are sometimes strong enough to alter the trajectories of charged particles in both solar wind and magnetospheric plasma. These particles, precipitate into the upper atmosphere and emit light. Digital Painting and video art 1080px x 1350x
